# Audio Files

Place the background music file here:
- Filename: `background-music.mp3`
- Format: MP3
- Duration: 2-3 minutes (will loop)
- Size: <2MB recommended

Recommended sources:
- Uppbeat: https://uppbeat.io/browse/collection/ambient-piano
- Bensound: https://www.bensound.com/royalty-free-music/ambient
- Pixabay: https://pixabay.com/music/search/ambient%20piano/
